		Window Parameters
			Receive Number: nType
		Window Variables
		Message Actions
			On SAM_CreateComplete
				If nType = nSelectedCustomers
					Set rbSelectedCustomers = TRUE
				Else
					Set rbAllCustomers = TRUE
				Return SalSendClassMessage( SAM_CreateComplete, wParam, lParam )
